          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pan to a medium-high heat with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>flattened chicken </strong>with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper </strong>and cook for 6 min on each side or until golden and cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
