    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>carrot & cabbage slaw mix</strong> to a bowl with your <strong>mayo</strong>, the juice of <strong>half</strong> your <strong>lime[s] </strong>(you'll use the rest later!) and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, <strong>pepper</strong> and <strong>sugar</strong> – this is your <strong>lime slaw</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
